{"id":"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor","title":"DefaultValueAccessor","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\", \"name\": \"DefaultValueAccessor\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/default_value_accessor.ts#L37-L126\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"defaultvalueaccessor\">DefaultValueAccessor<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#defaultvalueaccessor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a1kevbwem4q8uhtgsldvp7kig\">預設的 <code><a href=\"api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ControlValueAccessor</a></code>，用於寫入值並監聽輸入元素的更改。該訪問器供 <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControlDirective\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControlDirective</a></code>\n、<code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControlName</a></code> 和 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModel</a></code> 指令使用。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code>ReactiveFormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code>FormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>input<i>:not([type=checkbox])</i>[<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code><a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">textarea</a>[<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input<i>:not([type=checkbox])</i>[formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code><a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">textarea</a>[formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input<i>:not([type=checkbox])</i>[<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code><a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">textarea</a>[<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngDefaultControl</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n\n    <h3 id=\"using-the-default-value-accessor\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b9scb7al7e43d1f18h42sy3ge\">使用預設值訪問器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#using-the-default-value-accessor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ceusb1pee3b6ra0602y2lmeip\">以下範例示範了如何使用輸入元素啟用預設值訪問器（在這種情況下為文字欄位）。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nconst firstNameControl = new <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a>();\n</code-example>\n<code-example>\n&lt;input type=\"text\" [formControl]=\"firstNameControl\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e1kmkj2eqgun1dvnvaey7wju2\">預設情況下，此值訪問器用於 <code>&lt;input type=\"text\"&gt;</code> 和 <code>&lt;<a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">textarea</a>&gt;</code> 元素，但你也可以將其用於具有類似行為且不需要特殊處理的自定義元件。為了將預設值訪問器附加到自定義元素，請新增 <code><a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngDefaultControl</a></code> 屬性，如下所示。</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;custom-input-component <a href=\"api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngDefaultControl</a> [(<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>)]=\"value\"&gt;&lt;/custom-input-component&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALUE_ACCESSOR\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - errors/NG01203\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/ControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#defaultvalueaccessor\n - api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#description\n - api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#selectors\n - api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#using-the-default-value-accessor\n - api/forms/DefaultValueAccessor#匯出自\n - api/forms/FormControl\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/default_value_accessor.ts#L37-L126\n-->"}